SPA (for a sample Ebook by a Sample Company) + User profile creation Using Stripe API (https://obscure-dawn-96338.herokuapp.com/)

Node.JS (express-handlebars) and Stripe API with default card payment element - https://stripe.com/docs/payments/payment-element; https://github.com/stripe/stripe-node

styling for navbar https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.3/components/navbar/

Deployment to Heroku 
